OL,3,CJail sentences handed out to those
OL,4,Cinvolved in Southampton disorder
OL,6,FA number of people have now been
OL,7,Fjailed for their parts in disorder in
OL,8,FSouthampton following the murder of
OL,9,FHenry Nowak.
OL,11,FThe university student was murdered by
OL,12,FVickrum Digwa in December 2025, using
OL,13,Fa knife prosecutors said he carried as
OL,14,Fpart of his Sikh religion.
OL,16,FAnger erupted after police body-worn
OL,17,Fvideo was released showing Mr Nowak
OL,18,Fbeing placed in handcuffs moments
OL,19,Fbefore he became unconscious and
OL,20,Fsubsequently died.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
