OL,3,CJail sentences handed out to those
OL,4,Cinvolved in Southampton disorder
OL,6,FIt prompted protests which descended
OL,7,Finto scenes of violent disorder on the
OL,8,Fstreets of Southampton, resulting in
OL,9,Finjuries to 11 Hampshire Police
OL,10,Fofficers and a police dog.
OL,12,FA crackdown by the force has since
OL,13,Fseen more than 20 people charged with
OL,14,Fvarious offences.
OL,16,FHere, ITV News Meridian collates a
OL,17,Flist of sentenced individuals involved
OL,18,Fin the unrest.
OL,20,FLeon O'Leary, 41
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
