OL,3,CJail sentences handed out to those
OL,4,Cinvolved in Southampton disorder
OL,6,FHe was recorded carrying a yellow
OL,7,Ftraffic cone, which he threw towards
OL,8,Fofficers.
OL,10,FDaniel Frost, 44
OL,12,FFather-of-two Frost, from Southampton,
OL,13,Fwas jailed for two years and four
OL,14,Fmonths for violent disorder and
OL,15,Fpossessing an offensive weapon.
OL,17,FHe'd fashioned a dog lead with a metal
OL,18,Fcarabiner into a "makeshift
OL,19,Fknuckleduster".
OL,21,FReece Robinson, 21
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
