OL,4,Cinvolved in Southampton disorder
OL,6,FRobinson, of Havant, was jailed for
OL,7,Ftwo years for violent disorder.
OL,9,FHe threw two stones or small bricks
OL,10,Fduring the protest in the Portswood
OL,11,Farea, a court heard.
